        <tr><td><strong>Temperature</strong></td><td>Below 20°C = low mosquito & fly activity;<br>20°C–35°C = favorable mosquito activity;<br>28°C–40°C = moderate fly activity potential;<br>Above 40°C + humidity &lt;30% reduces mosquito & fly activity except near shaded waste, farms, livestock, organic matter.</td></tr>
