        <tr><td><strong>Wind Speed (ULV spraying)</strong></td><td>Below 10 km/h = Suitable;<br>10–15 km/h = Use with caution;<br>Above 15 km/h = Suspend ULV operations.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Pest Development Timing</strong></td><td>After rainfall/leakage/standing water:<br>- Mosquito larvae: 3–5 days<br>- Adult mosquitoes: 5–10 days<br>- Complaints: 7–14 days<br>Fly increase in farms/waste/livestock: 5–10 days if sanitation worsens.<br>Fly risk high only if environmental conditions support sustained breeding.</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
